snippet.title: Danganronpa Antebellum: Official Trailer (A Danganronpa Fangame)
snippet.description:
15 of you have committed a crime... we shall cure you of your sins.

Thank you to everyone who helped with the prologue and trailer!
Thanks so much to @LyrineChippo on twitter for some of the splash art and cg art in this trailer and we are very excited to unveil the prologue.

Discord: https://discord.gg/NZtFznY4jy
Instagram: @Danganronpa_Antebellum
